                     <interp inst="t18220911-288-person2613" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I was in Penton-street, and heard the alarm. I saw the prisoner running in a direction from the cry. I found him in custody. At the time I took hold of him, he had the coat - he did not say how he came by it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220911-288-person2614">
